24:22.235 --> 24:25.940
Just maybe I had bad pizza the night before.

24:26.781 --> 24:32.027
Maybe I drank a little too much sacramental wine and just the, you know, I had a bad dream.

24:33.870 --> 24:40.498
All he had to hold on to through all that his life had gone through was these dreams that he was holding on to.

24:43.010 --> 24:55.745
See, that would cause any of us to question whether or not we had really heard from God, but Joseph's story shows us that even when circumstances seem dire, in jail, no thoughts of getting out.

24:56.365 --> 25:00.450
Only the, hey, when you get out tomorrow, will you remember me?

