And the dude didn't.

25:03.954 --> 25:06.917
It was a couple of years before, oh, hey, wait a minute.

25:08.119 --> 25:10.962
Fair, I got a guy a couple of years ago in jail.

25:15.170 --> 25:17.694
God's vision is always toward a greater purpose.

25:18.435 --> 25:41.554
Despite the betrayal, despite the slavery, despite the imprisonment, Joseph's faithfulness led to a position where not only could he affect change in his own life, but he saved the lives of thousands of Egyptians, but ultimately he saved the lives of his own brothers and his dad, his family,

25:42.690 --> 25:53.665
But without all of the difficulty, without all of the trials, without all of the scariest of being in jail, none of that would have come to fruition.

25:55.668 --> 26:01.475
