26:01.736 --> 26:12.210
You look at Paul being in jail, Silas, Peter, in jail, locked up for us in our modern society, that would be for a lot of us, that would be the end.

26:12.450 --> 26:28.807
That would kind of be the kind of a closing to a lot of our situation because in our society, being a convict or an ex-convict once you got out, carries certain stigma, makes jobs getting harder, things of that nature.

26:28.847 --> 26:36.474
It makes even being a believer sometimes people kind of doubt whether or not you're sincere, even if you've had a genuine experience.

26:38.917 --> 26:40.018
See, as a church,

26:41.346 --> 26:45.812
