29:30.882 --> 29:33.744
hope and healing to our community.

29:34.125 --> 29:39.530
See, God initiates the work, but we're called to participate actively in it.

29:39.570 --> 29:41.271
Here's that word active again.

29:41.631 --> 29:47.657
Paul reminds the Philippian church that the good work begun in them was God's doing.

29:48.037 --> 29:54.082
It required their, but it required their continued partnership in faith and in action.

29:54.362 --> 30:00.868
There has been too much abdication of our role in the community.

30:00.848 --> 30:05.013
the society to take over the job of the church.

30:07.496 --> 30:08.658
Ooh, that didn't get amends.

30:08.978 --> 30:10.720
That's okay.

