30:53.954 --> 30:56.037
See God's work isn't a solo effort.

30:56.118 --> 31:00.505
It's a collaborative mission where he invites people to join in.

31:01.146 --> 31:18.354
Our role is to respond to God's initiation and God's invitation with faithfulness, engaging in that service that he's called us to, engaging in outreach and in community building as active participants in his plan.

31:19.554 --> 31:24.261
Building a hope means investing in relationships and in community.

31:24.502 --> 31:29.649
Just as Jesus invested in his disciples, we're called to pour into others.

31:29.690 --> 31:32.734
