32:09.982 --> 32:10.203
No.

32:11.724 --> 32:13.266
Saying how beautiful are you?

32:14.434 --> 32:21.002
that you go out into a lost and dying world and you take the most beautifully fragrant flower.

32:22.303 --> 32:23.164
That is Jesus.

32:24.266 --> 32:28.090
