32:49.493 --> 32:56.062
Discipleship, mentoring, and community involvement are foundational to the kingdom work that we're called to.

32:56.082 --> 32:56.823
Did you hear those?

32:57.404 --> 33:02.090
Discipleship, mentoring, and community involvement.

33:03.572 --> 33:10.642
We cannot be a church that only exists inside the four walls of 3, 2, 2, 4, Russell Boulevard.

33:11.938 --> 33:13.145
We cannot be.

