33:23.021 --> 33:27.265
We have to be bringing people outside the four walls inside here.

33:27.605 --> 33:47.346
So whether that means that we're offering coaching classes, mentoring programs, if we are going and taking ourselves and putting an arm around a young person or another brother or sister who needs to be uplifted, who we need to lift their arms, whatever it may be, whether we need to be

