38:26.583 --> 38:34.295
We all love Jesus, and if you'll come and join us, you can be another person that helps hold us accountable, and we'll walk forward together in Jesus, amen?

38:35.457 --> 38:39.543
See, true hope is sustained by God's love through the Holy Spirit.

38:39.783 --> 38:46.834
When we talk about having problems, our hope is sustained through the power of the Holy Spirit.

38:48.834 --> 38:52.379
