41:10.708 --> 41:12.410
That's an active faith.

41:13.071 --> 41:15.474
That's an active participation.

41:18.530 --> 41:20.974
I want to see Berea temple persevere.

41:21.414 --> 41:34.334
No matter the challenges that we face, our community needs to see that our hope is resilient, not because of our strength, but because of the love of God that anchors us.

41:37.078 --> 41:45.170
I can tell you with most surety because I've been the one to receive the word.

41:47.234 --> 41:53.722
What is happening at Maria Temple over the last three years is being noticed by our community.

