43:56.287 --> 43:58.569
So now we need to continue that process.

43:58.889 --> 44:04.095
We need to continue acting as the body of Christ in a lost and dying world.

44:04.575 --> 44:05.636
It is working.

44:05.696 --> 44:06.277
It is calling.

44:06.297 --> 44:07.538
