44:17.470 --> 44:26.866
As we close today, I want us to remember that we're not only called to offer hope and healing, we're called to build a future where hope

44:27.106 --> 44:30.171
can be found and healing can happen.

44:30.491 --> 44:32.053
We're called to trust God's vision.

44:32.113 --> 44:34.357
We're called to partner with Him in His work.

44:34.377 --> 44:38.423
We're called to persevere in hope despite the challenges.

44:40.846 --> 44:50.140
As we embrace this identity that we're building out this whole, we are A.G. church members who offer hope and healing to our community.

44:51.683 --> 44:56.690
I hope that we will be filled with the courage to make this a reality.

44:57.538 --> 45:07.851
that we will be filled with the Spirit to make this kind of body of believers at the corner of Compton and Russell a reality, to make this actually happen.

45:08.151 --> 45:14.699
