45:53.378 --> 46:00.847
by all means in every conversation, in every encounter, in every divine appointment that you provide for us.

46:01.128 --> 46:08.918
May Berea Temple be a lighthouse, a beacon of hope to those passing through the darkness into your glorious light.

46:09.618 --> 46:13.704
In Jesus' name, amen, with every head bowed and every eye closed still.

46:15.025 --> 46:18.770
If you've never asked Jesus into your heart, I want to invite you to take that first step.

46:19.906 --> 46:27.534
Jesus offers hope and healing and a future filled with purpose for you specifically for today.

46:27.834 --> 46:30.577
