46:47.778 --> 46:52.868
will continue to pray with you, will continue to respond together.

46:52.928 --> 47:08.498
But for all those who are already believers, I want to encourage you to commit to trusting his vision, to partnering with him and persevering through whatever challenges you face.

47:09.602 --> 47:19.472
I want you to pray that we would be a community that embodies hope and healing in every conversation, in every encounter, and every divine appointment.

47:19.492 --> 47:30.002
So as our worship team sings, if you need a moment to pray, this one we're only gonna take a moment for response and as they sing.

47:31.063 --> 47:37.810
And then we're gonna go into a special time of prayer with a separate special song for a few minutes.

47:38.050 --> 47:40.786
Amen, the altars are open.

